{"type": "article", "id": 27237, "title": "可以旋转的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-24T06:49:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 86, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140239OjcQhpIm4bXBAqFa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你想要一盏“爱玩儿”的台灯，维也纳的双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.bonpart.at/\">bonpart</a> 推出的 <a href=\"http://www.bonpart.at/bonpart---lupo.html\">lupo</a> 会让你眼前一亮。它的造型可以说是极其简洁，仅由框架和折叠的金属灯罩组成。尽管简单，bonpart 并不想让它过于单调，两片灯罩都可以独立转动，营造出各式各样的光影效果。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140236etHblA1WzVITpEFu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140237snX0B4xWhkwKoSDO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.28239609\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021402373unZI4eimPHFkbWs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44621027\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140238B3Jfc1qoZY6S9rWC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70285714\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}